---
---

<section class="section-cool" id="systems">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="kicker">What we build</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Five core systems.<br/>Infinite hours recovered.</h2>
    <p class="subhead section-sub" style={{marginBottom: 56}}>
      We don't sell software. We build the operational backbone that runs your business while you focus on growth.
    </p>
    <div class="bento">
      <div class="bento-card colspan-3 rowspan-2 brand">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">CRM Infrastructure</div>
          <div class="b-sub">
            A solid CRM is the backbone of every scalable business. We build it right — so every lead is automatically structured, tagged, and scored without anyone lifting a finger.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style={{display:'flex', gap:8, marginTop:24, flexWrap:'wrap'}}>
          <span class="b-chip">Auto lead scoring</span>
          <span class="b-chip">Consistent naming conventions</span>
          <span class="b-chip">Pipeline automation</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card colspan-3">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 8.81 19.79 19.79 0 01.02 2.18 2 2 0 012 0h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 7.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 14v2.92z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">Lead Capture</div>
          <div class="b-sub">Every inquiry from every channel flows automatically into your CRM. No more manual copy-paste, no more lost leads from slow response times.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card colspan-3 dark">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">Lead Nurture</div>
          <div class="b-sub">Prospects who don't book immediately get systematically engaged with personalized touchpoints — dramatically reducing no-shows and building trust before the call.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card colspan-2">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="23 7 16 12 23 17 23 7"/><rect x="1" y="5" width="15" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">Transcript Analysis</div>
        </div>
        <div class="b-sub">Every sales call auto-recorded, transcribed, and analyzed. Get strategic insights without reviewing a single recording yourself.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card colspan-2">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">Client Onboarding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="b-sub">From signed contract to full access — automated. Resources created, comms sent, permissions set the moment ink dries.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card colspan-2">
        <div>
          <div class="b-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="b-title">Always On</div>
        </div>
        <div class="b-sub">No queue, no shift change. Your systems run 24/7 with under 24-hour response to any issue, guaranteed.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
